{"tid":178071,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[巴打入]朝早起身d頭髮成日彈起，點搞？","createTime":"2017-03-29T09:46:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T00:47:56.000Z","uid":29774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3f967e8af4caa1a4d0ed7400f2d13008288f9bb1","tid":178071,"uid":29774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T09:46:21.000Z","msg":"特別係後腦既頭髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用水濕佢都冇用，仲搞到個頭睇落無啦啦濕左一達<br />\n洗頭又太花時間<br />\n<br />\n點搞好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a56ada24863ef068cf1f8ef268320c9ef64a2dd","tid":178071,"uid":71710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T09:50:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>特別係後腦既頭髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用水濕佢都冇用，仲搞到個頭睇落無啦啦濕左一達<br />\n洗頭又太花時間<br />\n<br />\n點搞好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用水應該要濕到頭皮至得&hellip;"},{"pid":"8ef7e1951a2a50fe9a46b82bc48cc9461ae1a2e9","tid":178071,"uid":2113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T09:50:38.000Z","msg":"由佢"},{"pid":"bb2aaefb1b4639458a42e4813f5c3bb715c03cd2","tid":178071,"uid":34647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T09:51:02.000Z","msg":"留長/直接沖涼"},{"pid":"261af726fe4100ba0a618141ecbb2d47a6e74d63","tid":178071,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T09:51:38.000Z","msg":"吹頭"},{"pid":"32ed14b72bb4083e328e992b8a2a16c3de04ab53","tid":178071,"uid":37585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T09:51:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>特別係後腦既頭髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用水濕佢都冇用，仲搞到個頭睇落無啦啦濕左一達<br />\n洗頭又太花時間<br />\n<br />\n點搞好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用花灑濕個頭唔洗一分鐘"},{"pid":"3d765b5417c7c9f8b07e0720050a0878f80163a1","tid":178071,"uid