4,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T10:53:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前中學時期成日都會彈起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但廿歲之後冇左呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 轉左髮型？"},{"pid":"c82e1765e4babad5cd9c30e678e0a24171fbefb7","tid":178071,"uid":29774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T11:05:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://cdn1.cdnme.se/2427527/7-3/2014-04-29-0922_535f5338e087c310dc2c9ddc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.cdnme.se%2F2427527%2F7-3%2F2014-04-29-0922_535f5338e087c310dc2c9ddc.jpg&h=33a65881&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f0f51c0012d988c76c995a522c14c1ec0d3e3c2","tid":178071,"uid":22949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T11:08:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以前中學時期成日都會彈起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但廿歲之後冇左呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 轉左髮型？</blockquote><br />\n畢左業幾年都冇轉過型 應該話根本唔理佢<br />\n我都唔知點解會無啦啦冇事 好奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8587ec1dbaab8e92b273471e7e79aab336d834a","tid":178071,"uid":67778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T11:09:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以前中學時期成日都會彈起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但廿歲之後冇左呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 轉左髮型？</blockquote><br />\n畢左業幾年都冇轉過型 應該話根本唔理佢<br />\n我都唔知點解會無啦啦冇事 好奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係，以前個頭成個撒亞人咁，25過後日日都死魚頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10a4fc85fe558082bce59a512f8d06e299140c57","tid":178071,"uid":40512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T11:17:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ab5540e5996e1533b64908248af9275a2599b7","tid":178071,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T11:23:36.000Z","msg":"用花灑沖濕佢捽吓咪搞掂囉， 咁簡單都講咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81872e57c9a41d68993c4508b454dc65cfcab839","tid":178071,"uid":25899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T11:25:31.000Z","msg":"靚仔＝天然呆<br />\n唔靚仔＝早D起身洗頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa5a6ee5d2b6756cba00a8774a42e077854ccee","tid":178071,"uid":18977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T11:27:39.000Z","msg":"洗頭 收獲唔使代價？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18329f3dbf52af3ac1ffa3c2b3df9437bbbb3c1a","tid":178071,"uid":38395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T11:49:03.000Z","msg":"用梳濕水梳下會好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/no